{
  "stem": "16313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we tried to have some maybe visas to United State or something, you know, it doesn't go through.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because there was a special quota for Polish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you wait for a visa, you can wait 100 years before they can go, have a visa.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sometimes, by good luck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yes, we tried, and this doesn't help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's affected this way-- they got a treaty, in fact.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Polacks make a treaty with Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this treaty, they make all kind-- I mean, it's got commerce and something like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, the Germans got a plan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They got a treaty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they got a plan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this way they give it some money under the table to this [INAUDIBLE], [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they do the job against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This way boiling up-- there's more boiling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, not the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When they-- when the war don't start in September 1st, '39, there were big pogroms in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The situation start to be very-- very dangerous for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in life I belonged to organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was thinking, [INAUDIBLE] some day I go to Israel and-- and fight for Israel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We was prepared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got the organization goal, call this Brit HaHayal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every Jew-- not every Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jewish people, what they finish the Polish service in the Polish army who want belong to our organization, the Brit HaHayal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This mean like, veterans here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, it's not veterans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They're people, what finish the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They know how to handle arms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some day we think the situation was be better, we be prepared morally, physically, and can handle arms, in case when we need it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the idea of our leader.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The leader was Ze'ev Jobtinsky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you hear about the name of Ze'ev Jobtinsky.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
